overview: Shot on location in Beverly Hills and Palm Beach, Dynastud 3 carries on in the grand tradition of its predecessors with lavish production values and the hottest new talent that money can buy. Mr. Carrington (Matt Bradshaw) is back in action, this time at the opulent South Bay Club Hotel, where he's checked himself into the plush Penthouse in order to find his "true self." On his spiritual quest he finds plenty of physical gratification from some of the sexiest men alive, in the form of the hotel's well-endowed help and wealthy guests. But most importantly, Carrington discovers that money isn't everything... From a wet and wild shower three-way to an exotic encounter on a private beach, Dynastud 3 is a pounding, pulsing, penetrating sex vacation of the highest calibre.
tagline: Some men are created more equal than others...
title: Dynastud 3: South Beach
